rComments: Absolutely fantastic prof, really cares about the success of his students and is passionate about the material. Loves his trusses.

Bruun really is the best prof you could ask for, clear lectures, relevant notes and great feedback. On top of this he is super down to earth and gives off the impression that he genuinely cares for his students. The only cons are that his problem sets and quizzes are easy compaired to the exam and therefore don't prep you as well as they could.
Very clear and organized lectures. Makes very good notes on the board.

He's wonderful, caring, and genuine. He never ridicules you even if you ask him to explain the simplest concepts. Wonderful guy and would definitely take his course again! Never skip lectures because his lectures aren't recorded, and his in-class notes are very helpful.

Amazing Prof! -Extremely knowledgeable and has a passion for what he is teaching -The best lectures out of all sections hands down -Responds to emails quickly and also is willing to help students after class/ during office hours -However, compared to the exams, his problem sets were way too easy Would take his course again! :)
